Myrtle Watkins https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Myrtle_Watkins 0 Myrtle Watkins (23 June 1908 – 10 November 1968) was an American-born Mexican dancer, jazz and Latin American music singer, and actress, who came to be known in the United States and Mexico as Paquita Zarate.
